{"tid":2381786,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登廢除特朗普禁令 准許變性人參軍服役","createTime":"2021-01-26T23:51:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T14:05:22.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"de09eaa75d114c68383567e96b1320453a031c7c","tid":2381786,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T23:51:03.000Z","msg":"美國總統拜登繼續簽署行政命令，周一推翻了前任特朗普的禁令，准許變性人在美軍服役。<br />\n<br />\n拜登的行政命令即時禁止任何非自願退伍、開除或因性別認同擔憂而拒絕他人入伍的行為。白宮在聲明表示：「總統認為性別認同不應該成為參軍的障礙，美國的力量在於其多元性。允許所有合格的美國軍人為他們的國家服務，對軍隊和國家都更好，因為一個包容性的軍隊才更有效。簡單而言，這是正確的事情，也符合我們的國家利益。」<br />\n<br />\n前總統奧巴馬在2016年首次允許變性人參軍，還允許他們在服役期間進行變性手術時得到醫療照顧。但特朗普上任後，在2018年發佈限制變性人在軍隊服役備忘錄，指變性軍人將導致「巨大的醫療成本和混亂」。現時變性人在美國軍隊服役的人數不明確，但據一些倡導組織表示，可能達1.5萬人。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210126/3VB3BQLIV5CAPIZTM2FUZKBGDM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210126%2F3VB3BQLIV5CAPIZTM2FUZKBGDM%2F&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSv8wCZVYJieBIKSEfzXA%2FSmA%3D&h=f206e91a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210126%2F3VB3BQLIV5CAPIZTM2FUZKBGDM%2F&h=b2915ff5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210126/3VB3BQLIV5CAPIZTM2FUZKBGDM/</a>"},{"pid":"fb0167ca2d4b10f07d1406194d25aaf8a7691ed9","tid":2381786,"uid":183758,"like":12,"dislike":10,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T23:54:33.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">變性人=變態撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"ce9992b2bb3660c6caca77a6ce9683f0a9589c3b","tid":2381786,"uid":165361,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T23:57:20.000Z","msg":"好快有淫亂軍營新聞"},{"pid":"4f07d8cd118e8a112da9c1b3ffe56b127f8a0833","tid":2381786,"uid":32667,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T23:58:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/no